{"tid":1185343,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"李家誠：未有具體計劃發展香檳大廈","createTime":"2019-06-04T08:22:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-04T09:29:57.000Z","uid":228995,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1c4ae0a225e8e3ca46784842fcf68f63eb1c09e4","tid":1185343,"uid":228995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T08:22:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190604/large/1559627103_a718.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190604%2Flarge%2F1559627103_a718.jpg&h=b14f3734&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n//美麗華酒店（071）舉行股東周年大會，主席兼行政總裁李家誠表示，恒地（012）暫未考慮如何發展已收購香檳大廈的業權，而美麗華亦只持有其中一層，兩家公司未就此問題討論。<br />\n<br />\n對於人民幣貶值，李家誠指，今年來港旅客仍有增長，加上酒店客人國際化，估計人幣貶值影響不大。副行政總裁黃烈初補充，人幣對公司資金組合的佔比不多，因此其波幅對公司財務狀況影響不大。 //<br />\n<br />\n浪費一樓一資源<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6233357eec415fad8316cd00709932357aee1c6","tid":1185343,"uid":20867,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T09:26:19.000Z","msg":"大劉：THE ONE<br />\n恆地：THE ONE FOUR ONE"},{"pid":"6ff7343c8c0231579590ff1e8a01f429c80b5fe7","tid":1185343,"uid":46042,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T09:29:57.000Z","msg":"建興大廈呢"}]}